show.description: A passionate romantic drama about Rohan and Ananya: their love story begins in college, ends in a breakup, and eight years later they collide again—this time with a secret child between them. When Rohan returns as a superstar cricketer, a hidden truth emerges—his son. This story is woven with love, revenge, guilt, and second chances, where emotions flare as intensely as any match on the pitch. But after facing the truth, will their love triumph once more? Watch Now!
